{"tid":60310,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"（直播）菠蘿青瓜雞柳，薑蔥蠔！","createTime":"2016-12-30T10:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T17:43:39.000Z","uid":7293,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1c444caa8f8dd64485b808b3e97382a94112e49","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/184452_7003d1cef9bf0f83a60e3e47bb0b996d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F184452_7003d1cef9bf0f83a60e3e47bb0b996d.jpg&h=a61aae49&s={SIZE}\" />雞柳解凍印乾"},{"pid":"f4d68c7b6db25e01afc05c05c8ce8006a66a3b61","tid":60310,"uid":4874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/184452_7003d1cef9bf0f83a60e3e47bb0b996d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F184452_7003d1cef9bf0f83a60e3e47bb0b996d.jpg&h=a61aae49&s={SIZE}\" />雞柳解凍印乾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知唔知咩係雞柳"},{"pid":"e771afa4410c656378dc831948c8266f41bf9c7f","tid":60310,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:51:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/184452_7003d1cef9bf0f83a60e3e47bb0b996d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F184452_7003d1cef9bf0f83a60e3e47bb0b996d.jpg&h=a61aae49&s={SIZE}\" />雞柳解凍印乾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知唔知咩係雞柳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9b32443f9df920e4c0b9677b28332712ecd6ad","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/184452_7003d1cef9bf0f83a60e3e47bb0b996d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F184452_7003d1cef9bf0f83a60e3e47bb0b996d.jpg&h=a61aae49&s={SIZE}\" />雞柳解凍印乾</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n知唔知咩係雞柳</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫菠蘿青瓜雞脾扒，ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4088fe0059ff831c00a50c08af84a868b1a23aa","tid":60310,"uid":35572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T10:57:33.000Z","msg":"一鍵留名"},{"pid":"3609021807ad7deffa27e6f565d1b1809432e032","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTb5eMTqwnG4BhoCchwAXLRar4PDrU9biJDvKh1YDAE4V?filename=6MDPKnM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MDPKnM.jpg&h=f7b36af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雞切細件，落生粉糖鹽胡椒醃下先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/191250_f2ecdfd23a5dea85b0d5be67ea4aebb6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F191250_f2ecdfd23a5dea85b0d5be67ea4aebb6.jpg&h=c3d75dba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同場解凍蠔<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/191251_eb872b2c7989daa207001ab16a5dfb1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F191251_eb872b2c7989daa207001ab16a5dfb1c.jpg&h=f6ada670&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青瓜切咗個頭落鹽打圈捽下就會無咗苦味<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaUPSsKhMChWcaLKVsFNTrbTiu2qtBuTanRtgTYfBS1a1?filename=768v6KL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F768v6KL.jpg&h=7f930813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n青瓜切條，菠蘿對切"},{"pid":"55f3d739e66661109c3d88670e72b114e9d964f3","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:17:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/191701_a0292d07ea15a6c176ffc4011dadd394.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F191701_a0292d07ea15a6c176ffc4011dadd394.jpg&h=9b10c2b2&s={SIZE}\" />落多少少油，油熱落雞唔好翻佢。我切得唔好，有大有細"},{"pid":"e34ebe0e49646717490af33a44f1bd3dc9e166eb","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:24:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmfWSq1UfzeYqN2t2DTFPwiPieYiC1k2ALp7AdiKVoM7u4?filename=W1GoPi0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW1GoPi0.jpg&h=86593f64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n煎到金黃色就翻轉～"},{"pid":"7c637719b3f3982817c4c61e7134e84fb53a560b","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:33:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/193206_8ca1d4d04127744be413a442af3bfc50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F193206_8ca1d4d04127744be413a442af3bfc50.jpg&h=04d610f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雞備用，用廚紙印走多餘油。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYhDiEjW7FXjdaNy6H57ozzqiauAHd6EJ3QUibmKKZxX2?filename=UovdwoB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUovdwoB.jpg&h=0818cae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蒜蓉薑起鑊炒青瓜"},{"pid":"f81b3d149d020a7a447eb2589d3772770eac638e","tid":60310,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:34:42.000Z","msg":"好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會直播食埋嗎？"},{"pid":"4a2d1696664928f30ae31f0356c18ba3f1ed6fcc","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:39:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmY8qJ9u2WsrLLjHhMX2EEbyaxKddKktJEPAsaJhEJuYfh?filename=68210XD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68210XD.jpg&h=4688149e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雞回鑊炒多陣，落埋菠蘿就食得啦～"},{"pid":"44c1b17b2909dd6ea2fb8cad9e5a6058fe82bce3","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:49:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmd3GwU166ifeP7yjBLnymcsMmXkeVoM1UWW3eYu67f9H9?filename=uxfq2DF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fuxfq2DF.jpg&h=23cc49a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蠔要用生粉洗乾淨，小心手指整爛隻蠔。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZ74B5mhqJZs3fkNdqxNNSyjLikwfugyv2Y7wXEoeFPVn?filename=Gr938hd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGr938hd.jpg&h=5b544e9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蠔洗完就飛水，記得水唔好滾起。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWX9zULH15FqgEJRvQUph1HGSrrF7nj5H3Nx8nRgSiui3?filename=EzA8qtZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEzA8qtZ.jpg&h=5942f551&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後用廚紙印乾，再準備一碟生粉"},{"pid":"ede92ab7ecf02e5045dfe1e82bca0b3421897d47","tid":60310,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T11:56:45.000Z","msg":"Live"},{"pid":"d9cee8d667010f077b7a956b5345067002296ba4","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZMijE5rBJzyLn3U4zapDMc1oY9o75Xc4qd73VWRRHeqM?filename=6yASPG6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yASPG6.jpg&h=31143f70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n薑片乾蔥起鑊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQ2fjrh8rqV31qhzgLwcc3RoCR3Q1hMFpftzE3boHqjGf?filename=Dc32V28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDc32V28.jpg&h=4fc63a18&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/195853_85ba89f9df88e0eca1cb9448cab1c052.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F195853_85ba89f9df88e0eca1cb9448cab1c052.jpg&h=f64ca54e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蠔要即撲生粉即落鑊，整定哂好易出水。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/30/195854_195071721e2f6b4ced111f1d31242c6e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F30%2F195854_195071721e2f6b4ced111f1d31242c6e.jpg&h=93ec2d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蠔煎到咁上下就落埋蔥，落黃酒"},{"pid":"4d2e8e4436848783d0ba0e86e42991a8685a2e87","tid":60310,"uid":53652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:03:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a97ccc5945fbe024efe172f34644ab6b27ab08b6","tid":60310,"uid":60256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:05:14.000Z","msg":"留名🐷🐷🐷"},{"pid":"83e02ed641c8036d5e9f84b8c6db0868f65d293c","tid":60310,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:06:10.000Z","msg":"蠔好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178c1e9387f239e4bdeaef0a668a28dcbb2342a2","tid":60310,"uid":8911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:09:35.000Z","msg":"黃酒邊處有，同煎幾成熟"},{"pid":"82d5fcd8131f18940b3ac820f2fb8b1b34b60fcf","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:12:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTUzGTZXczjSTZvfgN8d3nSDFKwhmBUosTJGCmqc3mqAb?filename=4E1756w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4E1756w.jpg&h=bcdf1196&s={SIZE}\" />最後一舊啦～"},{"pid":"29321002df1588997db67e602748a6a57addd3cf","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蠔好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n超正，有好多汁"},{"pid":"8ae715fc3af678a28f05023a2ffab89e9eea8e20","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:15:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黃酒邊處有，同煎幾成熟</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n黃酒即係一般廚酒，花雕紹興都係黃酒，一般雜貨鋪都有。"},{"pid":"acfe1cca37f13827fea4799730686c36f11d8b1b","tid":60310,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:15:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蠔好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n超正，有好多汁</blockquote><br />\n請我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外果碟菠蘿炒雞，對我好有意義<br />\n以前老豆老母未離婚<br />\n成日食呢個餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ebc08eceb678465fbbc7dc4a245e145aabe434","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:18:07.000Z","msg":"蠔要食得安全d，我食全熟。飛水個時我飛30秒，之後煎返個面做金黃，包熟～"},{"pid":"1efd77e08a01efebddc7cc8655292d6a6ccace77","tid":60310,"uid":7293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:20:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蠔好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n超正，有好多汁</blockquote><br />\n請我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外果碟菠蘿炒雞，對我好有意義<br />\n以前老豆老母未離婚<br />\n成日食呢個餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伯母仲有無咩拿手菜你好回味呀？我試下整呀～"},{"pid":"e5e2efe126c92a397dec3576e83484f61f344436","tid":60310,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T12:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蠔好正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n超正，有好多汁</blockquote><br />\n請我食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外果碟菠蘿炒雞，對我好有意義<br />\n以前老豆老母未離婚<br />\n成日食呢個餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n伯母仲有無咩拿手菜你好回味呀？我試下整呀～</blockquote><br />\n冇見佢好耐喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}